1. Project Initiation

      1.1 Define project objectives
      
      1.2 Conduct feasibility study
      
      1.3 Identify stakeholders

2. Project Planning

        2.1 Define project scope and deliverables
        
        2.2 Prepare work breakdown structure (WBS)
        
        2.3 Create project schedule and Gantt chart
        
        2.4 Identify resources and cost estimation
        
        2.5 Risk analysis and management plan

3. System Analysis

        3.1 Requirement gathering
        
        3.2 Requirement analysis
        
        3.3 Prepare Software Requirement Specification (SRS) document
        
        3.4 Review and approval of SRS

4. System Design

        4.1 Database design
        
        4.2 User Interface (UI) design
        
        4.3 System architecture design
        
        4.4 Design review
        
        4.5 Prepare design documentation

5. System Development

        5.1 Environment setup
        
        5.2 Frontend development
        
        5.3 Backend development
        
        5.4 Module integration
        
        5.5 Code review and optimization

6. Testing

      6.1 Prepare test plan and test cases
      
      6.2 Unit testing
      
      6.3 Integration testing
      
      6.4 System testing
      
      6.5 User Acceptance Testing (UAT)

7. Deployment & Implementation

      7.1 Deployment setup (server and hosting)
      
      7.2 Data migration
      
      7.3 User training
      
      7.4 Go-live approval and system handover

8. Maintenance & Support

        8.1 System monitoring
        
        8.2 Bug fixing and updates
        
        8.3 Performance tuning and optimization
